{"id":155392,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2011/05/用废热驱动汽车/","date":"2011-05-26T00:00:44Z","modified":"2011-05-26T00:00:44Z","title":"用废热驱动汽车","content":"<p>汽车卡车汽油中有至少三分之二的能量被以废热的形式浪费掉了。热电材料可把废热转变成电力，燃油经济性提高至少5%。但材料的昂贵加上转换效率的低下，使其难以有实际应用。现在，研究人员正在商业汽车和SUV上组装测试首台热电发动机原型。测试汽车包括宝马、福特和雪佛兰。 加州热电设备制造商BSST没有使用常见热电材料碲化铋，因为铋比较昂贵，而且工作温度最高只有250°C。他们改用了铪和锆的混合物，能工作在更高温度下，使发动机效率能提高大约40%。计算机模拟显示，雪佛兰安装这种原型发电站后，燃油经济性提高3%。<img border=\"0\" height=\"1\" src=\"http://solidot.org.feedsportal.com/c/33236/f/556826/s/1536206e/mf.gif\" width=\"1\" /></p>\n<div>\n<table border=\"0\">\n<tr>\n<td valign=\"middle\"><a href=\"http://res.feedsportal.com/viral/sendemail2.html?title=%E7%94%A8%E5%BA%9F%E7%83%AD%E9%A9%B1%E5%8A%A8%E6%B1%BD%E8%BD%A6&#038;link=http%3A%2F%2Fhardware.solidot.org%2Farticle.pl%3Fsid%3D11%2F05%2F25%2F117236%26amp%3Bfrom%3Drss\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://res3.feedsportal.com/images/emailthis2.gif\" /></a></td>\n<td valign=\"middle\"><a href=\"http://res.feedsportal.com/viral/bookmark.cfm?title=%E7%94%A8%E5%BA%9F%E7%83%AD%E9%A9%B1%E5%8A%A8%E6%B1%BD%E8%BD%A6&#038;link=http%3A%2F%2Fhardware.solidot.org%2Farticle.pl%3Fsid%3D11%2F05%2F25%2F117236%26amp%3Bfrom%3Drss\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://res3.feedsportal.com/images/bookmark.gif\" /></a></td>\n</tr>\n</table>\n</div>\n<p><a href=\"http://da.feedsportal.com/r/101094064746/u/49/f/556826/c/33236/s/1536206e/a2.htm\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://da.feedsportal.com/r/101094064746/u/49/f/556826/c/33236/s/1536206e/a2.img\" /></a></p>\n<div>\n<a href=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/solidot?a=xF2zWQG8-k0:Nki02Sh_RqA:yIl2AUoC8zA\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/solidot?d=yIl2AUoC8zA\" /></a> <a href=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/solidot?a=xF2zWQG8-k0:Nki02Sh_RqA:7Q72WNTAKBA\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/solidot?d=7Q72WNTAKBA\" /></a>\n</div>\n</p>\n<p><small>本文由自动聚合程序取自网络，内容和观点不代表数字时代立场</small></p>\n<form method=\"POST\" action=\"http://www.feedblitz.c